## 2) Release notes

**Title:** `v1.0.0 — Architecture MVP`

```md
## v1.0.0 — Architecture MVP

This release marks the completion of the core architectural foundation of the MiniBank Ledger API.

### Included
- Clean Architecture structure (Domain / Application / Infrastructure / API)
- CQRS pattern via MediatR (Commands/Queries)
- EF Core + SQLite persistence
- Migrations support
- REST endpoints for transactions and basic reporting
- Tests + GitHub Actions CI build pipeline

### Notes
This is the architectural baseline intended for growth into a production-ready system (auth, validation, logging, Docker, PostgreSQL).
